This Project tries to tackle down a big issue in the Natural language processing domain of tackling hate speech by classifying the dataset into sincere or unsincere catagory.
The Neural Networks are perfectly capable of learning text emotions from labelled dataset and we aim to utilize this capabilty.
Usiing Hugging Face's Emotion dataset which contains 20,000 labelled tweets to train and test our Neural network to be able to classify unseen tweets.
The Preprocessing of the dataset includes Tokenization
